stalking my prey theres a throne about 10 feet high i climb on 
and off the top of several times that took quite a bit of getting 
used to particularly since im not fond of heights the first 
rehearsal was a disaster i couldnt breathe or sing 
the thing that bothers me the most now is that the throne 
tends to rattle and shake a bit that can be real unnerving 
cheek isnt sure he overcame his fear of heights but his 
motivation is sufficient to send him scrambling up the throne 
saving enough breath to sing im willing to try almost 
anything he said 
