restructuring program aimed at focusing the companys resources on 
its transportation businesses officials announced today 
csx officials said the company would repurchase up to 60 million 
common shares and sell the companys natural gas transmission and 
natural gas liquids processing businesses texas gas transmission 
corp of owensboro ky and csx ngl corp of houston 
