prices ranging from 28 to 33 per share for their holdings the 
company will then select a single purchase price and will buy up to 
40 million shares offered at or below that price 
the offer is being mailed to shareholders this week and will 
close oct 18 csx spokesman thomas e hoppin said 
the company then may repurchase the remainder of the 60 million 
shares approximately 38 percent of its oustanding shares in the 
open market or in private negotiations officials said 
at 33 a share the buyback would cost csx 198 billion 
initial funding for the repurchase will come from cash and 
shortterm borrowings 
