who need a faster compatible unit it is also being introduced in 
direct competition with international business machines corps 
personal system2 model 70121 which is comparably sized and 
priced compaq said 
the deskpro incorporates compaqs flex architecture in a smaller 
form offering compatibility with the industry standard while 
running 25 percent faster than the ibm ps2 model 70121 canion 
said 
the models range in price from 5199 to 7999 
the 386 is short for the 80386 intel corps most powerful 
microprocessor and the successor to the intel 80286 
</TEXT>
