shares without selling assets but he called the planned sale of 
csxs natural gas transmission and natural gas liquids processing 
businesses texas gas transmission corp of owensboro ky and csx 
ngl corp of houston a sound business move 
the restructuring continues csxs moves over the past year to 
reduce costs by making payroll cuts and selling assets geller 
said csx said it will considering selling additional assets such 
as its luxury resort properties and will launch an aggressive 
program designed to significantly reduce operating and overhead 
costs 
